  [Text] Tokyo, June 17 KYODO -- Defense Agency chief 
Atsushi Kanda has decided to appoint Noboru Hoshuyama, currently 
director of the agency's secretariat, as director general of the 
Defense Facilities Administration Agency, Defense Agency sources 
