BFN 

  [Text] Police General Prathin Santipraphop, director 
general of the Police Department, this evening called on and 
held talks with Lieutenant Commander Chalat Worachat in front of 
the National Assembly building. 
  Pol. Gen. Prathin told reporters that Lt. Cdr. Chalat agreed 
to receive medical treatment at the Police Hospital after he 
addressed the gathering of 2,000 people at about 1830 and after 
