<H3> <TI>   Fighting Between Forces Reported </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Fighting Between Forces Reported </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   BK1906131294 Bangkok SIAM RAT in Thai 19 Jun 94 p 15 </F>
<F P=103> BK1906131294 </F>
<F P=104>  Bangkok SIAM RAT </F>
<F P=105>  Thai </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] According to a report, 1,200 Burmese Government 
soldiers attacked the Khun Sa military stronghold in Chot Town 
on 17 June. They advanced to the center of the town and 
encountered strong opposition by Khun Sa soldiers. 
  At 1000 on 18 June, Burmese helicopters fired rockets and 
heavy machineguns at the Khun Sa force northeast of Chot Town. 
There were no reports of the battle or casualties. 

</TEXT>

