<F P=102>   SK1706114594 Pyongyang KCNA in English 1110 GMT 17 Jun 94 </F>
<F P=103> SK1706114594 </F>
<F P=104>  Pyongyang KCNA </F>
<F P=105>  English </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] Pyongyang, June 17 (KCNA) -- Secretary of the C.C. 
[Central Committee], the Workers' Party of Korea [WPK] Hwang 
Chang-yop today met and conversed in a friendly atmosphere with 
a delegation of the Japan Liberal Democratic Party [LDP] headed 
by Taku Yamasaki, deputy secretary general of the party and 
member of the house of representatives, at the Mansudae Assembly 
Hall. 
  Present there was vice department director of the WPK 
Central 
Committee Kim Yang-kon. 

</TEXT>

