<H3> <TI>   Paper Denounces ROK Document on Nuclear Issue </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Paper Denounces ROK Document on Nuclear Issue </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   SK1906105794 Pyongyang KCNA in English 1037 GMT 19 Jun 94 </F>
