<H4>    Need To Verify Nuclear Programs </H4>

<F P=102> OW2006045594 Tokyo NHK General Television Network in 
Japanese 0300 GMT 20 Jun 94 </F>

<F P=103> OW2006045594 </F>
<F P=104>  Tokyo NHK General Television Network </F>
<F P=105>  Japanese </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

<F P=106> [Statement by Foreign Minister Koji Kakizawa at the House of </F>
Councillors' Foreign Affairs Committee on 20 June -- recorded] 
  [Text] I believe it is quite impossible for the United 
States to take the position of ignoring altogether what has 
occurred in the past. On Japan's part, as members of this 
committee just pointed out, since the production of nuclear 
weapons on the Korean peninsula represents a direct threat, we 
maintain that there is a need to continue efforts to verify even 
the past operational records of nuclear reactors. 

</TEXT>

