<F P=102>   BK2006071794 Phnom Penh National Radio of Cambodia Network 
in Cambodian 0500 GMT 20 Jun 94 </F>

<F P=103> BK2006071794 </F>
<F P=104>  Phnom Penh National Radio of Cambodia Network 
in Cambodian 0500 GMT 20 Jun 94 </F>

<F P=105> Cambodian </F>


